      "category": "Trail",
      "description": "Super Light. Super Legs. Silence. Our \"SL\" stands for a number of things – all with the same goal: you and your bike in nature and the feeling of the perfect ride. First and foremost, the Sresh SL was developed as a pure trail rocket. Light, agile, balanced, and with a tuned PRO10 chassis that always delivers maximum grip and support. 350 watts of power? It's hard to believe that this bike really contains that much power. Integrated with the utmost subtlety, the innovative drive system is practically unnoticeable visually and acoustically. But it offers you more. More range, more crazy climbs, more remote trails – and yet it's still a mountain bike. FAST BY NATURE – DRIVEN BY INSTINCT &nbsp; &nbsp;",
